  "body": "If a signature is invalid nil is returned at https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/develop/core/types/transaction.go#L120\n\nThis propagates up to address conversion, generating the zero (but valid) 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 address. If this address was previously sent some wei it can be spent by an unsigned tx, causing a consensus failure.\n\nFix: reject all txs with invalid signatures.\n",
